{"tid":1328013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嬲到訓唔到，有曬4個證據比你睇張超雄重提逃犯條例","createTime":"2019-07-17T19:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T00:46:55.000Z","uid":46352,"like":2,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5b58661279b1ecaa8b046660078141c18e36b283","tid":1328013,"uid":46352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:34:55.000Z","msg":"唔比comment ，你地鐘意話我分化就分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nCCTVB<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥宣布政府修訂《逃犯條例》「壽終正寢」，工黨立法會議員張超雄提交修訂《逃犯條例》私人草案。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄表示，他提出修訂，讓香港可以與大陸或澳門以外的地方互交逃犯，已取得律政司法律草擬專員發出的證明書，並提交予立法會主席。<br />\n<br />\n張超雄指，台灣殺人案的疑犯陳同佳將於十月獲釋，如要等立法會復會才審議草案，最快要十月第二個星期。他認為自己的草案內容相對簡單，希望主席召開特別會議處理，有望在陳同佳獲釋前完成修訂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5d2f3f02e603830034c5fdc4/%E5%BC%B5%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%84%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E4%BF%AE%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E4%BE%8B%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88-%E5%86%80%E5%8D%81%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5d2f3f02e603830034c5fdc4%2F%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E8%25B6%2585%25E9%259B%2584%25E6%258F%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%25A7%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%258D%2589%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%2586%2580%25E5%258D%2581%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2589%258D%25E5%25AE%258C%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E8%25A8%2582&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaaktVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=58d0eb21\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5d2f3f02e603830034c5fdc4/%E5%BC%B5%E8%B6%85%E9%9B%84%E6%8F%90%E4%BA%A4%E4%BF%AE%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E4%BE%8B%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E8%8D%89%E6%A1%88-%E5%86%80%E5%8D%81%E6%9C%88%E5%89%8D%E5%AE%8C%E6%88%90%E4%BF%AE%E8%A8%82</a><br />\n<br />\nHK01 <br />\n<br />\n《香港01》獲悉，除楊、尹外，有第三名民主派立法會議員，早前亦提出私人草案，建議修訂《逃犯條例》讓香港能與台灣作移交安排，草案已獲律政司發出證明書。不過，相關草案能否解決台灣殺人案問題，將陳同佳引渡到台灣受審，視乎政府如何回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/351384/01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E6%A1%88%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E7%88%B6%E8%A6%AA-6-26%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%8F%90%E5%9B%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%B1%82%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE?fbclid=IwAR1WKUNp5UMUJimNE4A3qxcxpJkaxb7scqaQ_wZDplSBUEnrrX68VS1FW2A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%259F%25A5%2F351384%2F01%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25BD%25B3%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2588%25B6%25E8%25A6%25AA-6-26%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2587%25BD%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD-%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E6%25B1%2582%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1WKUNp5UMUJimNE4A3qxcxpJkaxb7scqaQ_wZDplSBUEnrrX68VS1FW2A&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaaktVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=40c02ab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/351384/01%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6-%E9%99%B3%E5%90%8C%E4%BD%B3%E6%A1%88%E6%AD%BB%E8%80%85%E7%88%B6%E8%A6%AA-6-26%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD-%E4%B8%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%8F%90%E5%9B%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E6%B1%82%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE?fbclid=IwAR1WKUNp5UMUJimNE4A3qxcxpJkaxb7scqaQ_wZDplSBUEnrrX68VS1FW2A</a><br />\n<br />\n明報<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qnObyFx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqnObyFx.png&h=39786199&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vaZRyFy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvaZRyFy.png&h=0bbecf02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ni-CABLE <br />\n<br />\n有報道指，台灣殺人案家屬曾致函特首林鄭月娥，提出四個方案移交疑犯陳同佳，保安局表示與家屬聯繫的事情不宜公開。 <br />\n<br />\n有報道指，死者潘曉穎的父母在六月底、即政府宣布暫緩修《逃犯條例》後，曾致函林鄭月娥提出四個方案，包括賦權香港法庭審理單一個案，以行政指令方式單次移交疑犯，賦予香港法庭域外法權，以及勸說疑犯陳同佳到台灣自首。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員楊岳橋、尹兆堅及張超雄分別提交私人草案，建議修訂《侵害人身罪》、《刑事司法管轄權條例》，及以單次個案方式移交疑犯到台灣，張超雄表示已獲律政司發出證明書。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/552822/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%93%9A%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%80%A1%E5%9B%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%BA%A4%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F552822%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2587%25BD%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2580%25A1%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258A%25AF&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaaktVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=2f408a93\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F552822%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2587%25BD%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%2580%25A1%25E5%259B%259B%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258A%25AF&h=1d17be6b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/552822/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E6%93%9A%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E5%80%A1%E5%9B%9B%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88%E4%BA%A4%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF</a>"},{"pid":"e2e8eba53a008ffeb24e1398b9612d991f871009","tid":1328013,"uid":46352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:36:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90424538fdf12a6bb5053f58a7c6e178113e8eb","tid":1328013,"uid":34047,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:38:14.000Z","msg":"我覺得大家要再了解件事多啲 睇睇究竟張超雄個版本係點 再判斷下<br />\n<br />\n但有班人係唔係都屈人搞分化<br />\n真係令人好反感<br />\n本身根本大家冇搞分化<br />\n只係有啲野覺得有問題就提出<br />\n但就會比人屈你三毛同分化<br />\n<br />\n雨革果時質疑大台<br />\n都已經比人屈係熱狗<br />\n明明都唔係撐熱狗"},{"pid":"cc7cfc11e05762f312aeb9f0954208b3f0147beb","tid":1328013,"uid":209609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"reply